Description: GNOME overlay for LLM-powered text tone rewriting
 Castword is a GNOME overlay that rewrites selected text in any tone
 using LLM providers (OpenAI, Anthropic, Google Gemini, Ollama).
 Activate it with a keyboard shortcut, pick a tone, and the rewritten
 text is placed in your clipboard or typed inline.
